text: "Hemorrhage (In My Hands)" is a song by American hard rock band Fuel. It is the leading single from their second studio album Something Like Human. It went to number 30 in the United States and number 46 in Australia. ==Track listing== #"Hemorrhage (In My Hands)" #"Easy" #"Stripped Away" #"Going to California" (Led Zeppelin cover, written by Jimmy Page, Robert Plant) ==References== Category:2000 songs Category:2000s ballads Category:Rock ballads Category:Fuel (band) songs
